From 115663a52dcaef53c91547907f45cc4ffa385537 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Chris Liddell <chris.liddell@artifex.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Dec 2021 15:54:27 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] oss-fuzz 42280: Don't try to use a pdfi context with no
 stream

If setting the pdfi input stream from Postscript fails, also throw errors on
any other PDF operators that would access the input stream
---
 psi/zpdfops.c | 382 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++------------------------
 1 file changed, 197 insertions(+), 185 deletions(-)

